Using mock and stub objects
Testing private and protected methods
Looking for weak spots in your testing, with code coverage
Testing inherited projects', 'PHP', '', '', 0, 100, 'kamy');
INSERT INTO ikamych.links (id, name, web_address, description, category, sub_category_1, sub_category_2, privacy, rank, username) VALUES (55, 'Fundamentals with Simon Allardice', 'http://www.lynda.com/JavaScript-tutorials/Foundations-of-Programming-Fundamentals/83603-2.html', 'This course provides the core knowledge to begin programming in any language. Simon Allardice uses JavaScript to explore the core syntax of a programming language, and shows how to write and execute your first application and understand what''s going on under the hood. The course covers creating small programs to explore conditions, loops, variables, and expressions; working with different kinds of data and seeing how they affect memory; writing modular code; and how to debug, all using different approaches to constructing software applications.

